POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (50): NIGERIA (BAUCHI), CIRCULATING VACCINE-DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2, ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES, PAKISTAN (SINDH) FOLLOW-UP INFORMATION
*********************************************************************************************************************************************************
